How to create S3 buckets
------------------------

Create bucket
Options>General Purpose
bucket name: edu-mlops-020-bkt
choose bucket
ACL disable
block public access to -disable
- cn access from internet

bucket versioning enable
i
default encryption
bucket key - enable
bucket name - leave default
block
remove checkbox
